snippet.title: LITTLE HELLIONS - Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
THROW AWAY YOUR FRIENDS in this passive aggressive fighter where you can’t fight! Coming to Steam Early Access October 31st, 2022.

Demo available NOW.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2104110/Little_Hellions/
